02:01:13.120 --> 02:01:20.960
Well, I'm honored and pleased that you've taken the time

02:01:20.960 --> 02:01:26.240
to talk to me and about sharing my experiences

02:01:26.240 --> 02:01:28.960
in terms of what the intent of Congress was

02:01:28.960 --> 02:01:35.280
in terms of sharing the contributions of folks

02:01:35.280 --> 02:01:42.680
with different backgrounds that have been ignored over the years.

02:01:42.680 --> 02:01:48.760
The way I like to learn a little bit more about the end product

02:01:48.760 --> 02:01:53.040
in terms of the distribution of that and how we can make it

02:01:53.040 --> 02:01:58.080
more accessible to, because as I said before,

02:01:58.080 --> 02:02:01.240
education is really what opens the eyes,

02:02:01.240 --> 02:02:07.960
opens the minds of folks that don't have a full understanding

02:02:07.960 --> 02:02:14.080
of our complete society and not like to know how we can get it

02:02:14.080 --> 02:02:19.680
into the hands of those that need it that should get

02:02:19.680 --> 02:02:25.520
full enlightened and be more informed of the contributions

02:02:25.520 --> 02:02:29.880
of other folks that have done that maybe not speak their language

02:02:29.880 --> 02:02:34.040
or live in their neighborhoods, but are here to contribute

02:02:34.040 --> 02:02:36.160
to make this country greater.

02:02:36.160 --> 02:02:38.440
I think that's a great point when we can talk about that.

02:02:38.440 --> 02:02:40.480
So that's what I'm interested in.

02:02:40.480 --> 02:02:43.400
That's why I agreed to participate.

